data.description: Welcome to this amazing 6-bedroom, 5.2-bathroom home within the prestigious gated  Royal Melbourne Subdivision. Situated on a prime golf course lot, this home boasts unparalleled views of the lush conservancy and the enchanting 17th green.    Key Features include tumbled limestone and hardwood floors throughout, meticulously crafted crown moldings and custom millwork, a front Turret with a captivating winding staircase.  The Chef's kitchen boasts custom cabinets, granite countertops, top-of-the-line appliances, a generously sized Island with seating and a spacious eating area with large bay windows showcasing the gorgeous golf course view.  The Great room, with its striking stone fireplace, offers a warm and inviting sanctuary.  A first-floor bedroom, complete with an adjacent full bath, provides convenience and flexibility.  The primary suite is a true oasis, featuring a cozy fireplace, a luxurious bathroom and a private balcony to enjoy the stunning golf course and conservancy views.  The second floor unveils 3 additional spacious bedrooms, two full baths and a huge two-story bonus room that lends a unique and versatile space to the home.  The spacious finished English lower level is an entertainer's dream, housing a sprawling recreation room, bar room, exercise room, and a 6th bedroom with a full bath.   An amazing three-season room, with slate floors and a beautiful stone fireplace, extends your living space and offers a tranquil retreat.  Step outside to discover the grand paver patio, hot tub, and inviting fire pit area-perfect for gatherings and relaxation.  The beautifully landscaped yard showcases breathtaking golf course and prairie views.  New Generator Backup!!  So many many new home components, upgrades and special features...see Feature List for details!!   This home, a true testament to craftsmanship and design excellence, delivers luxury and comfort in every corner. Located within the nationally ranked Stevenson High School District and award-winning elementary and middle schools.   This residence resides in Royal Melbourne Subdivision-a gated community that offers 24/7 security and prestige.    Don't let this extraordinary opportunity slip away. Make this magnificent home yours and indulge in the lifestyle you deserve!
